metadata.name: Digital Reflection 001
metadata.description:
001 from a series of analogue experimental videos of digital interfaces. The series has been taken from a body of research which explores the space between the physical and digital. 

1 of 5 remaining copies of the 'Digital Reflections' publication may be redeemed by the buyer upon purchase.
